上门给妻子做了笔录，也调取了高空摄像头的监控，但因为是晚上的缘故，视频不太清晰，只能看到一条白色弧线。孙先生前往派出所做笔录时，被告知技术人员正在分析监控录像，警方也提取了芝麻油瓶上的指纹、 DNA 等信息。 上游新闻记者在社交平台发现，相关帖子的热度很高，第一条帖子就有 4.2 万次点赞，8600 多条评论，5 条帖子累计有 2 万评论。不少网友表示，建议孙先生起诉整栋楼。「太坏了，高空抛物就是谋杀」「还好没砸到头，不幸中的万幸」… 怀孕 34 周孕妇被高空抛下玻璃瓶砸断两根脚趾，警方：DNA 采集已结束，正在分析 _ 孙先生 _ 妻子 _ 上游"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-6cd22db1ca6a4b8b5f7a27fd69ab702c_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "2.5 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/665808337"}}, "attached_info": "CkAImPufquD9rcQxEAMaCTExMDIzNTExOCC8qcu2BjAAOKUBQBtyCTY2NTgwODMzN3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1725238034.828503", "card_id": "Q_665549091", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 133}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "做完《原神》5.0 纳塔剧情，你有什么感想？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-d71f2e34df88567ac5857336c8ab0a7b_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "2.5 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/665549091"}}, "attached_info": "CkAImPufquD9rcQxEAMaCTExMDE3NzI2NSDix7y2BjAAOMIBQBxyCTY2NTU0OTA5MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1725238034.828851", "card_id": "Q_665465095", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 95}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "马上开学了，孩子还没写完作业不想补怎么办？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-1ae6d42a56a7c3c12bec20371fda5c45_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "2.4 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/665